Name: Average time for Accepted + Assigned across all process variants containing this activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in Accepted + Assigned when followed by Completed + In Call versus when followed by Completed + Resolved
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Assigned in variants that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Name: Cycle time of Accepted + Assigned grouped by country
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Time from Accepted + Assigned to Completed + In Call in variants where both activities occur consecutively
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Time between Queued + Awaiting Assignment and Accepted + Assigned in variants that later lead to Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Elapsed time from case start to Accepted + Assigned in cases that eventually perform Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Time of Accepted + Assigned when it occurs after an Accepted + Wait - User versus after a Queued + Awaiting Assignment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Total time for Accepted + Assigned in the variant: Accepted + In Progress → Accepted + In Progress → Queued + Awaiting Assignment → Accepted + In Progress → Accepted + Assigned → Accepted + In Progress → Completed + Resolved → Completed + Closed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + Resolved occurs

Name: Time from Accepted + Assigned to the next occurrence of Accepted + In Progress in variants that include Completed + In Call downstream
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Time between Accepted + Assigned and Completed + In Call when they appear in the same case but not consecutively
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Assigned in high-frequency variants (frequency > 100) that do not contain Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Name: Time from the prior Accepted + In Progress to Accepted + Assigned in variants that later execute Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Total duration of Accepted + Assigned across all cases that also contain Completed + In Call, regardless of order
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Cycle time of Accepted + Assigned in cases handled by resource groups in France compared to Brazil
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and the end of case grouped by the last value of resource country
